The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy is designed to transform individuals into cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. This 16-week program includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course also covers risk management and compliance with international standards such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Instruction is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop